5. DNS .

time <- c(254, 2834, 674, 155)
name <- c("Google Public DNS", "Cloudflare",  "Open DNS", "DNS ")

DNS <- data.frame(Name= name, Time = time)

barplot(DNS$Time, names.arg = DNS$Name, col = "olivedrab3")
